TX is a simple game engine I wrote for a uni project.
It is written in C++, OpenGL. Uses MiniXML, QT, Lua, LuaBind, DevIL and rcbc for COLLADA model parsing/rendering.

To build:
=========
scons

Usage:
======
./tx

The following libraries are required:
=====================================
rcbc (see https://github.com/dcbishop/)
glut (freeglut3-dev)
libluabind-dev
liblua5.1-0-dev
libmxml-dev
libdevil-dev
